hopobject.body: Who do you work for? farmacianunesdesa.com Clearing can also benefit students who get higher grades than they had expected. Known as Adjustment, it allows them to try to secure a place on a course with higher entry requirements. Students can register to use the Adjustment system — which is available for two weeks, from results day on August 15 until August 31 — so that universities can view their application. During this time their original confirmed place will still be held open for them.
